  "texts": [
    "If the user does not include the string {{text}} in the template, the input text will be appended to the prompt template.Prompt output parsing.",
    "To run users' prompts, Wordflow supports remote LLM API services, such as GPT 4 [41] and Gemini [57] API services provided by OpenAI and Google, as well as local open-source models, such as Llama 2 [59] and Phi 2 [1].",
    "Users can set their preferred models in the Setting Panel (Fig. 4).",
    "After receiving the output from the LLM API service or local model, the Editor View applies Myer's diffing algorithm [21,39] to compare the output text with the input text.",
    "It then highlights the changes made by the LLM (e.g., addition, replacement, and deletion) using different text background colors (Fig. 1A)."
  ],
